author: Doreen Christensen
title: Southwest fall sale with fares starting at $73
text:
Southwest fall sale with fares starting at $73 Southwest Airlines airfare sale runs through July 16. By Doreen Christensen Sun Sentinel 
Southwest Airlines is having a fall sale, offering one-way flights as low as $73. 
Book flights for departure on any day except Friday and Saturday from Fort Lauderdale, West Palm Beach, Orlando, Baltimore, Connecticut and 80 other U.S. cities for travel on Aug. 25 through Dec. 16. 
For instance, fly from Fort Lauderdale to Philadelphia for $122. Go from Orlando to Atlanta for $89. 
Blackout dates: Sept. 3, 4, 7; Nov. 24-25; Nov. 28 - Dec. 1. Bonus: Bags fly free.
